Create dummy users database in tibble format

Source: R/zzz.R
create_dummy_users.Rd

Create dummy users database in tibble format

create_dummy_users()

Value

a tibble with five columns: date_created, username, password, name, email, and permissions.

Examples


users_base <- create_dummy_users()
str(users_base)
